rows.label: qev087401_MSG0002
rows.name: Hey, sorry to bother ya—can you spare a cup of joe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Sure thing, Commander.
You're becoming quite the regular here lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0004
rows.name: Mustache man has too much time on his wings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0005
rows.name: Maybe, but that's a good thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0006
rows.name:
If the brass has time to putz around,
it means the rest of the force is runnin' smooth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0007
rows.name: Maybe—or maybe it means the brass is playing hooky.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0008
rows.name: Hey, yeah! Where do I sign up for a cushy job like that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_SEL0011
rows.name: Claim that even Tatsu could do Vandham's job.

rows.label: qev087401_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that only Vandham could do his job.

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0009
rows.name:
Oh ho, is that right?
You all got no idea about my job, do ya?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0010
rows.name: Well, at least SOMEONE gets it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0011
rows.name: But you other jokers, you got no idea what it's like, do ya?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0012
rows.name: Well, maybe it's time you all walked a mile in my boots![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0013
rows.name:
Er, I don't know what that means,
but I don't like the sound of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087401_MSG0014
rows.name:
Well that's just too damn bad, ain't it?
Meet me first thing in the morning, and that's an order.[ST:wait ]
